// Balance shortcut pressed?
  //Yes:
    // Pitch < 0, > 0, or == 0?
      // Pitch == 0:
        // Yes: Cut motors, deploy brakes, end balancing program
      // Pitch < 0:
        // Move robot backwards on x-axis
          // Is pitch beginning to shift?
           // No: Continue moving backwards
           // Yes: Cut motors, deploy brakes, end balancing program
      // Pitch > 0:
        // Move robot forwards on x-axis
         // Is pitch beginning to shift?
          // No: Continue moving forwards
          // Yes: Cut motors, deploy brakes, end balancing program
